{"type":"message","id":"0bb37bdd","parentId":"9e145275","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:45:32.266Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The context monitor shows that we're at 75% usage (150,100 / 200,000 tokens), which exceeds the 60% threshold. The session key is agent:main:main.\n\nI should check if there are any significant items in the recent memory files to consolidate, and consider if we need to do any memory consolidation before suggesting a session reset. But the cron job is just a monitor - I should just log this and potentially alert if this is a recurring pattern or severe issue.\n\nLet me just report this in the log and HEARTBEAT_OK - but actually this is a cron job context monitor running, so it's checking the context. I should just note the findings.\n\nActually, looking at this more carefully - this is an automated cron job context monitor. It found that context usage is at 75%, which exceeds the 60% threshold. The appropriate response is just to log this and potentially save any important context. But since this is an automated job, I should just let it be and perhaps suggest starting a new session at some point when Sir is around.\n\nFor now, since this is a cron job context monitor that just ran and reported - I should just note this is informational and might want to follow up. But actually, looking at the runtime - it's \"agent=main\" and the context is mine (the main agent session). The monitor is warning that context is at 75%.\n\nLet me just report this in a minimal way since it's a cron job. The context monitor found something worth noting. I'll just acknowledge the finding.","thinkingSignature":"664b2a22c75570c66418b7ba67fde8dc0bf640905f5a98a6ba1bcfbdafeb776f"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n📊 **Context Monitor Report** (19:45)\n\n| Metric | Value |\n|--------|-------|\n| Context Usage | **75%** (150,100 / 200,000 tokens) |\n| Threshold | 60% |\n| Status | ⚠️ Exceeded |\n\n建议 Sir 空闲时开启新 session 以重置上下文，或整理 MEMORY-LITE.md 精简长期记忆。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1366,"output":403,"cacheRead":37011,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38780,"cost":{"input":0.0005464,"output":0.0006045,"cacheRead":0.00148044,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0026313400000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773920720493}}
